Except for its age (in Mei 10 years) I have it hooked op to an external receiver. In this case a Denon AVR-1610 (Thanks to Moyoweb back in the days).

The receiver now constantly is shooting into short circuit protection as some kind of issue.

The strange part is that I have all new cables and there are no "real" shorts, and when I think I have fixed it it shoots into protection again.

Hopefully I have now fixed by disconnecting all the connected wires. Keep you posted.
